export const endpoints = {

    REFRESHTOKEN: `${baseURL}api/token/refresh/`,

    GETUSERFILES: `${baseURL}files/user/`,
    GETUSERFILE: `${baseURL}files/`,

    GETADMINDATA: `${baseURL}files/admin/`,
